    <section name="Create document type">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to create a document type, to define the structure
                              of a class of similar documents.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=0;
    toppx=160;
    bottompx=610;
   </script>
   <div class='group'> 
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/inars/create_documenttype.png" alt='Create document type screenshot'/> 
    </div></div>
    <p>
     Creation of <a href='../concepts/documenttype.html'>document type</a> with name 'myhobby',
     in namespace 'snp'. The namespace 'snp' already contains the document type 'upcoming'.
    </p>
   </div>

   <p>
    To add a documenttype to a <a href='../concepts/namespace.html'>namespace</a>, select the
    <a href='../concepts/namespaces_folder.html'>folder</a> for that namespace
    as the <a href='../../contributors/concepts/current_folder.html'>current folder</a> and
    select 'create new type' in the <a href='../../contributors/concepts/folder_action_menu.html'>folder action menu</a>.
    A dialog window appears.
   </p>
   <p>
    Type an informative name for the documenttype.
   </p>

